WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.710
Hey, good morning family. I'm excited to

00:00:02.720 --> 00:00:05.190
be with you all today. I

00:00:05.200 --> 00:00:07.749
really truly am. We want to start

00:00:07.759 --> 00:00:11.190
a new channel. I feel in my

00:00:11.190 --> 00:00:11.200
heart—I

00:00:11.200 --> 00:00:13.830
have a lot of people that have

00:00:13.840 --> 00:00:17.189
wanted to sponsor and do things with

00:00:17.199 --> 00:00:20.310
this channel, but the Lord told me

00:00:20.320 --> 00:00:24.550
never allow people who were trying

00:00:24.560 --> 00:00:27.109
to sell a product to be on this channel.

00:00:27.119 --> 00:00:28.950
Now, I thought about putting anointing

00:00:28.960 --> 00:00:30.550
oils and things like that because you

00:00:30.560 --> 00:00:32.310
asked for it—anything that has to do

00:00:32.320 --> 00:00:34.389
with the church, but nothing like

00:00:34.399 --> 00:00:36.790
t-shirts and things like that. Does that

00:00:36.800 --> 00:00:39.110
make sense? I've dedicated this channel

00:00:39.120 --> 00:00:41.910
to the Father so that He has an avenue to

00:00:41.920 --> 00:00:44.389
speak to His people, whether He wants to

00:00:44.399 --> 00:00:46.389
speak through me or if He gives me a

00:00:46.399 --> 00:00:48.869
word through somebody

00:00:48.869 --> 00:00:48.879
else—like

00:00:48.879 --> 00:00:50.389
those last two words

00:00:50.399 --> 00:00:52.869
that lined up with what He gave me

00:00:52.879 --> 00:00:54.630
prophetically already. So,

00:00:54.640 --> 00:00:56.470
we've been praying, and my wife

00:00:56.480 --> 00:01:00.069
is really good at doing eBay. We're

00:01:00.079 --> 00:01:01.510
starting a channel and just

00:01:01.520 --> 00:01:03.270
announcing it now. If you want to follow

00:01:03.280 --> 00:01:05.350
it, fine. If you don't, fine. But we're

00:01:05.360 --> 00:01:07.030
going to be doing a channel. It's a blog

00:01:07.040 --> 00:01:10.149
channel, an everyday channel, as

00:01:10.159 --> 00:01:12.230
much as my wife is able to because

00:01:12.240 --> 00:01:13.910
she homeschools the kids and stuff. It's

00:01:13.920 --> 00:01:16.070
a lot of work

00:01:16.080 --> 00:01:17.429
homeschooling and doing all the things

00:01:17.439 --> 00:01:19.510
we do because we have a

00:01:19.520 --> 00:01:22.550
teenager, Braden. The channel's name is

00:01:22.560 --> 00:01:25.670
Come Thrift with Me. Our

00:01:25.680 --> 00:01:28.469
goal for 2024

00:01:28.479 --> 00:01:31.069
is teaching people how to do a side

00:01:31.079 --> 00:01:33.429
hustle. There's a lot of

00:01:33.439 --> 00:01:35.590
people I see who are struggling

00:01:35.600 --> 00:01:37.429
financially. I'm not saying I have

00:01:37.439 --> 00:01:40.149
it all together, y'all, but I trust God

00:01:40.159 --> 00:01:43.190
and I believe for everything I have. And

00:01:43.200 --> 00:01:45.910
He has provided a lot through Poshmark

00:01:45.920 --> 00:01:48.710
and through eBay. He gives me

00:01:48.720 --> 00:01:50.469
places; He'll tell me where to go find

00:01:50.479 --> 00:01:52.630
the merchandise, the t-shirts, the

00:01:52.640 --> 00:01:55.270
shoes, or whatever. I pray in the car. I

00:01:55.280 --> 00:01:57.270
ask God, 'Show me where do we go today,

00:01:57.270 --> 00:01:57.280
Father,'and

00:01:57.280 --> 00:01:59.190
I'm going to do that. I'm

00:01:59.200 --> 00:02:00.870
going to film it. I want to show you

00:02:00.880 --> 00:02:02.950
all how I use the prophetic gifting that

00:02:02.960 --> 00:02:05.109
God's given me—seeing

00:02:05.109 --> 00:02:05.119
and knowing—and

00:02:05.119 --> 00:02:08.150
how I use it to apply

00:02:08.160 --> 00:02:11.430
to everyday life.

00:02:11.440 --> 00:02:13.190
People think it's always

00:02:13.190 --> 00:02:13.200
hyper-spiritual,

00:02:13.200 --> 00:02:15.830
but I'm just a real person

00:02:15.830 --> 00:02:15.840
who

00:02:15.840 --> 00:02:18.630
has real needs and needs

00:02:18.640 --> 00:02:20.790
bills met every single day. Just like

00:02:20.790 --> 00:02:20.800
everyone,

00:02:20.800 --> 00:02:22.630
once a month, you

00:02:22.640 --> 00:02:24.390
pay your electric, water, gas,

00:02:24.400 --> 00:02:25.670
your mortgage,

00:02:25.670 --> 00:02:25.680
and

00:02:25.680 --> 00:02:27.670
your car payment; you've got to pay for

00:02:27.670 --> 00:02:27.680
that

00:02:27.680 --> 00:02:29.589
stuff unless you're debt-free, which some

00:02:29.599 --> 00:02:32.630
people are, but most of

00:02:32.640 --> 00:02:34.710
us aren't. And so, we have to believe

00:02:34.720 --> 00:02:36.630
for food. We have to believe for things.

00:02:36.640 --> 00:02:38.390
So, I'm going to show you all that side

00:02:38.400 --> 00:02:40.390
if you want to watch

00:02:40.400 --> 00:02:42.150
it. Some people might not

00:02:42.160 --> 00:02:43.509
care; they just want to hear the

00:02:43.519 --> 00:02:45.750
prophetic words and move on. But

00:02:45.760 --> 00:02:47.670
some people want to hear how to list on

00:02:47.680 --> 00:02:50.390
eBay, how my wife does inventory,

00:02:50.390 --> 00:02:50.400
and

00:02:50.400 --> 00:02:52.470
creative ideas to get extra

00:02:52.470 --> 00:02:52.480
wealth—doing

00:02:52.480 --> 00:02:55.589
things

00:02:55.599 --> 00:02:58.470
like thrifting, showing you

00:02:58.480 --> 00:03:00.390
what to buy,

00:03:00.400 --> 00:03:03.030
what not to buy, and what will sell for

00:03:03.040 --> 00:03:05.190
extra money. If you're interested

00:03:05.200 --> 00:03:07.030
in that and you want to come to our new

00:03:07.040 --> 00:03:09.350
channel, cool. The other

00:03:09.360 --> 00:03:11.190
part of it was the Lord put it on my

00:03:11.200 --> 00:03:13.030
heart to show

00:03:13.030 --> 00:03:13.040
you—I

00:03:13.040 --> 00:03:15.790
thought about making it fun—doing

00:03:15.790 --> 00:03:15.800
things

00:03:15.800 --> 00:03:18.710
I like, as I'm a gun enthusiast. I

00:03:18.720 --> 00:03:21.110
like guns and shooting

00:03:21.120 --> 00:03:23.509
and being out on the ranch with my

00:03:23.509 --> 00:03:23.519
dad

00:03:23.519 --> 00:03:26.309
and showing the Longhorn cattle and

00:03:26.319 --> 00:03:28.710
riding on the gator, going

00:03:28.720 --> 00:03:31.190
fishing,

00:03:31.200 --> 00:03:33.750
popping fireworks, or whatever.

00:03:33.760 --> 00:03:36.470
We have a place where we pop fireworks

00:03:36.480 --> 00:03:39.190
and camp,

00:03:39.200 --> 00:03:42.550
doing survival stuff. I'll show you what to

00:03:42.560 --> 00:03:45.789
do with your relatives that are left

00:03:45.799 --> 00:03:50.070
behind, leaving things for them,

00:03:50.070 --> 00:03:50.080
and

00:03:50.080 --> 00:03:53.030
showing you silver coins to barter

00:03:53.030 --> 00:03:53.040
with—which

00:03:53.040 --> 00:03:56.630
I feel in my spirit. Now, some of

00:03:56.630 --> 00:03:56.640
you may

00:03:56.640 --> 00:03:57.830
want to argue about

00:03:57.840 --> 00:03:59.589
it, and that's fine, but I'm telling you, I

00:03:59.599 --> 00:04:01.270
believe we're going to see some

00:04:01.280 --> 00:04:03.589
things ahead. I believe with all my

00:04:03.599 --> 00:04:05.750
heart you need bartering things:

00:04:05.760 --> 00:04:09.589
bartering food,

00:04:09.599 --> 00:04:11.750
silver, or

00:04:11.760 --> 00:04:15.990
maybe some gold little

00:04:15.990 --> 00:04:16.000
Krugerrands.

00:04:16.000 --> 00:04:18.710
I just have

00:04:18.720 --> 00:04:21.670
ideas the Lord has given me

00:04:21.670 --> 00:04:21.680
for

00:04:21.680 --> 00:04:24.950
a blog. I also wanted to

00:04:24.960 --> 00:04:28.390
update you on my weight loss.

00:04:28.400 --> 00:04:31.270
I've been

00:04:31.280 --> 00:04:32.870
praying. There were so many different

00:04:32.880 --> 00:04:36.710
ideas about what we should be eating:

00:04:40.479 --> 00:04:42.150
the carnivore diet, the

00:04:42.160 --> 00:04:44.629
keto diet, Mediterranean keto, all these

00:04:44.639 --> 00:04:48.550
different things.

00:04:48.560 --> 00:04:51.670
The first part of January,

00:04:51.680 --> 00:04:54.070
detoxing from all the sugar I used

00:04:54.080 --> 00:04:56.510
to consume was

00:04:56.520 --> 00:04:59.350
brutal. I thought I

00:04:59.350 --> 00:04:59.360
wasn't

00:04:59.360 --> 00:05:00.390
going to make it through this, but the

00:05:00.400 --> 00:05:01.590
Lord kept saying, 'You don't have a

00:05:01.600 --> 00:05:04.950
choice. You've got to do this.'So I

00:05:04.960 --> 00:05:06.870
went into prayer and fasting, started

00:05:06.880 --> 00:05:08.310
doing intermittent fasting, and started

00:05:08.320 --> 00:05:10.629
interceding. One day, the Lord spoke

00:05:10.639 --> 00:05:12.390
to me—I think it was around

00:05:12.400 --> 00:05:14.950
January 10th. He said to me,

00:05:14.950 --> 00:05:14.960
because

00:05:14.960 --> 00:05:16.790
I said, 'Lord, I'm doing carnivore and

00:05:16.800 --> 00:05:19.550
I'm not losing anything. What's going

00:05:19.550 --> 00:05:19.560
on?'I

00:05:19.560 --> 00:05:22.950
was eating a ton of meat all

00:05:22.960 --> 00:05:25.590
day long—steak,

00:05:25.590 --> 00:05:25.600
chicken—I

00:05:25.600 --> 00:05:29.430
would eat

00:05:29.440 --> 00:05:31.830
huge plates of meat. And the Lord spoke

00:05:31.840 --> 00:05:33.629
to me and said,

00:05:33.639 --> 00:05:37.029
'Brandon, it's about calories. You're

00:05:37.039 --> 00:05:39.830
eating way too much.'He said, 'Your

00:05:39.840 --> 00:05:42.230
body, even if you're on the carnivore

00:05:42.230 --> 00:05:42.240
diet,

00:05:42.240 --> 00:05:45.510
cannot burn off all the food

00:05:45.520 --> 00:05:48.150
that you're consuming. So, you need to

00:05:48.160 --> 00:05:52.070
go back to monitoring how many calories

00:05:52.080 --> 00:05:54.790
you are consuming on a day-to-day

00:05:54.790 --> 00:05:54.800
basis.'I

00:05:54.800 --> 00:05:57.189
started adding up how much steak,

00:05:57.199 --> 00:05:59.350
chicken, turkey, and meat

00:05:59.360 --> 00:06:01.430
I was eating, and I

00:06:01.430 --> 00:06:01.440
realized I was

00:06:01.440 --> 00:06:04.309
eating a ton

00:06:04.319 --> 00:06:06.150
of calories. That's why I

00:06:06.150 --> 00:06:06.160
wasn't

00:06:06.160 --> 00:06:07.430
losing weight; my body

00:06:07.430 --> 00:06:07.440
couldn't

00:06:07.440 --> 00:06:10.150
burn it all off. When

00:06:10.150 --> 00:06:10.160
it's

00:06:10.160 --> 00:06:12.309
as cold as it has been, I haven't

00:06:12.319 --> 00:06:14.710
been able to exercise outside, so of

00:06:14.720 --> 00:06:15.749
course you're not going to lose weight

00:06:15.749 --> 00:06:15.759
when

00:06:15.759 --> 00:06:18.150
consuming so much food.

00:06:18.160 --> 00:06:20.909
The Lord said, 'I want you to

00:06:20.919 --> 00:06:24.390
monitor every single day how many

00:06:24.400 --> 00:06:26.230
calories you are

00:06:26.230 --> 00:06:26.240
consuming.'So,

00:06:26.240 --> 00:06:30.150
I started

00:06:30.160 --> 00:06:34.189
keeping underneath 1,800

00:06:34.199 --> 00:06:38.070
calories. My wife,

00:06:38.080 --> 00:06:41.029
my little researcher,

00:06:43.039 --> 00:06:45.670
found an app

00:06:45.680 --> 00:06:49.110
that is phenomenal. It monitors

00:06:49.120 --> 00:06:50.710
your calories and tells you what

00:06:50.720 --> 00:06:52.550
you're eating. You can type in the

00:06:52.560 --> 00:06:54.629
restaurant, and it shows you exactly what's

00:06:54.639 --> 00:06:56.950
in it, along

00:06:56.950 --> 00:06:56.960
with

00:06:56.960 --> 00:06:58.550
your exercise and how

00:06:58.560 --> 00:07:00.309
many glasses of water you need

00:07:00.319 --> 00:07:02.390
every day. I think it was about 20

00:07:02.400 --> 00:07:04.469
dollars

00:07:07.510 --> 00:07:07.520
apiece.

00:07:11.199 --> 00:07:12.629
She's doing it with me to help

00:07:12.639 --> 00:07:14.790
motivate me and we're doing it together.

00:07:14.800 --> 00:07:16.629
She doesn't need to lose any weight, but

00:07:16.639 --> 00:07:19.189
she's such a blessing

00:07:19.189 --> 00:07:19.199
helping

00:07:19.199 --> 00:07:22.230
me log all the drinks and

00:07:22.240 --> 00:07:24.070
everything I do in a day.

00:07:28.319 --> 00:07:31.749
Keeping on track, I've lost

00:07:31.759 --> 00:07:36.150
14 pounds in the

00:07:36.160 --> 00:07:40.309
last three weeks. To God be the glory;

00:07:40.319 --> 00:07:42.870
I'm going in the right direction.

00:07:42.880 --> 00:07:44.950
It's not always been easy, but I'm

00:07:44.960 --> 00:07:46.629
drinking my

00:07:46.639 --> 00:07:49.350
diet shake

00:07:49.360 --> 00:07:51.110
and

00:07:51.110 --> 00:07:51.120
logging

00:07:51.120 --> 00:07:53.950
it.

00:07:53.960 --> 00:07:56.309
Instead of what I used to

00:07:56.319 --> 00:07:58.950
have for a snack,

00:07:58.950 --> 00:07:58.960
I'm

00:07:58.960 --> 00:08:03.309
just trying to find ways to make this

00:08:03.319 --> 00:08:05.830
a journey that's going to last

00:08:05.840 --> 00:08:07.749
forever, instead of something like

00:08:07.749 --> 00:08:07.759
a fad

00:08:07.759 --> 00:08:09.589
diet that I get burned out on as I

00:08:09.589 --> 00:08:09.599
have in

00:08:09.599 --> 00:08:11.510
the past. You lose a lot of

00:08:11.520 --> 00:08:13.270
weight and then you gain it all

00:08:13.280 --> 00:08:16.869
back. I said, 'God, show me how to make

00:08:16.879 --> 00:08:20.869
this a lifestyle. Help

00:08:20.869 --> 00:08:20.879
me.'I

00:08:20.879 --> 00:08:22.950
know a

00:08:22.960 --> 00:08:25.350
lot of people struggle with

00:08:25.360 --> 00:08:28.309
lifestyle changes that

00:08:28.309 --> 00:08:28.319
lead to

00:08:28.319 --> 00:08:30.950
yo-yo dieting, where you lose 100

00:08:30.960 --> 00:08:33.430
pounds like I'm after and then gain

00:08:33.440 --> 00:08:36.149
it all back. My goal is to have

00:08:36.159 --> 00:08:40.149
all of my weight off before October.

00:08:40.149 --> 00:08:40.159
The

00:08:40.159 --> 00:08:42.310
app

00:08:42.320 --> 00:08:43.829
even shows you that if you maintain

00:08:43.829 --> 00:08:43.839
these

00:08:43.839 --> 00:08:45.590
calories every single day,

00:08:45.590 --> 00:08:45.600
seven

00:08:45.600 --> 00:08:48.230
days a week, you will be at

00:08:48.240 --> 00:08:50.630
that weight by October. So, I thought it

00:08:50.640 --> 00:08:52.310
was really cool. So, I'm like, let's try

00:08:52.320 --> 00:08:55.190
it. I'm down 14

00:08:55.200 --> 00:08:57.190
pounds. So, I just wanted to

00:08:57.200 --> 00:08:58.870
update y'all on the weight loss

00:08:58.880 --> 00:09:00.630
and where I'm at with it. I told you

00:09:00.640 --> 00:09:02.630
I would. I didn't want to make it

00:09:02.640 --> 00:09:04.310
boring by coming out and telling you

00:09:04.320 --> 00:09:06.710
every single week. But maybe

00:09:06.720 --> 00:09:08.790
I'll put that on the blog

00:09:08.790 --> 00:09:08.800
channel—the

00:09:08.800 --> 00:09:10.230
other channel I told y'all about. The

00:09:10.240 --> 00:09:12.150
channels that we're starting, "Come

00:09:12.160 --> 00:09:16.829
Thrift With Me,"will be about prepping,

00:09:16.839 --> 00:09:20.230
thrifting, guns, and the fun things. Like I

00:09:20.240 --> 00:09:22.870
said, most people don't agree with

00:09:22.880 --> 00:09:25.110
carrying guns. Most people don't want to

00:09:25.120 --> 00:09:27.430
talk about them. Whatever.

00:09:27.440 --> 00:09:29.590
I personally carry a firearm with me

00:09:29.600 --> 00:09:32.310
wherever I go in this day and age

00:09:32.320 --> 00:09:34.150
with all these people acting crazy.

00:09:34.160 --> 00:09:35.509
People say, "Well, you should use Psalm

00:09:35.509 --> 00:09:35.519
91."I

00:09:35.519 --> 00:09:40.070
use both. I use Psalm 91 and

00:09:40.080 --> 00:09:42.550
I carry a sword at the same time. I make

00:09:42.560 --> 00:09:43.990
sure my wife and my children are

00:09:44.000 --> 00:09:46.870
protected at all costs. You know, I

00:09:46.880 --> 00:09:49.110
believe in my angels, but I also believe

00:09:49.120 --> 00:09:51.269
in the Second Amendment. And most people

00:09:51.279 --> 00:09:52.870
may not like that, but that's fine.

00:09:52.880 --> 00:09:54.870
That's between you and God. For me,

00:09:54.880 --> 00:09:57.509
I'm a Southerner. We live in the South,

00:09:57.519 --> 00:09:59.110
and I was raised with guns my whole

00:09:59.120 --> 00:10:01.350
life. My dad—this is the way our

00:10:01.360 --> 00:10:03.110
hunters were. We're fishers. We hunt.

00:10:03.120 --> 00:10:05.670
We fish. We do it all. That's just

00:10:05.680 --> 00:10:08.670
the way we are. And so

00:10:08.680 --> 00:10:11.269
most people don't like that, but

00:10:11.279 --> 00:10:12.949
you'll get over it. I mean, that's just

00:10:12.959 --> 00:10:15.269
the way it is. You

00:10:15.279 --> 00:10:17.509
know, we believe we have a right to

00:10:17.519 --> 00:10:20.550
defend ourselves and protect our families.

00:10:20.560 --> 00:10:23.990
And so, I'll show you about

00:10:24.000 --> 00:10:26.550
guns and things like that in

00:10:26.550 --> 00:10:26.560
another

00:10:26.560 --> 00:10:28.710
channel and about thrifting.

00:10:28.720 --> 00:10:31.990
It'll be a fun variety of stuff to

00:10:32.000 --> 00:10:35.509
watch. I want to keep this

00:10:35.519 --> 00:10:38.150
about prayer over here on this platform.

00:10:38.160 --> 00:10:39.750
If you want to stay, you can stay over

00:10:39.760 --> 00:10:41.190
here. It's going to be about prayer,

00:10:41.200 --> 00:10:42.949
intercessory prayer. It's going to be

00:10:42.959 --> 00:10:44.949
about the prophetic. It's going to be

00:10:44.959 --> 00:10:47.509
about everything the Lord gives me,

00:10:47.519 --> 00:10:49.750
bringing things and talking to you just

00:10:49.760 --> 00:10:51.829
like it is right now. But I just felt

00:10:51.839 --> 00:10:53.030
like I would add some other things

00:10:53.040 --> 00:10:55.670
because I'm telling you, through the

00:10:55.680 --> 00:10:58.550
spring, through the summer, going into

00:10:58.560 --> 00:11:01.470
the fall, there's going to become great

00:11:01.480 --> 00:11:04.069
suppression over freedom of speech a lot

00:11:04.079 --> 00:11:05.870
on these

00:11:05.880 --> 00:11:08.590
platforms. So, if I was to all of a

00:11:08.600 --> 00:11:12.230
sudden disappear from this channel, you would

